      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GARY INDIANA (8) is rarely out of the finish, recording 23 places from 44 starts. Has been in the money the last three starts, the latest when third (23.07) at this track. Solid beginner and with a good start should have clear running out wide. Overdue and expected to feature again. MISS ELPHABA (2) is rarely far away but tends to find one better, placing 11 from 22 starts. Better run when finding the frame last time though, finishing third (22.96) at this track. Smart beginner who should take advantage of the low draw. Winning chance. SANDI KINGDOM (1) ran a good time (15.98) when placing three back at this track but has missed the frame since, last time out finishing sixth (20.25) at Goulburn. Expecting sharp improvement this line-up. DOLLAR ROLEX (6) profiles nicely over this trip.",
